o ring in a retro adventure. You're just a green dot in the skies, but  that's all you need to be!\n\nFUNNY ARCHITECT: Try to build the biggest tower. The motto is: the biggest, not the highest... The higher you build the easier your tower will collapse.\n\nBe honest! WHERE DO YOU SEE YOURSELF IN 5 YEARS? Still stuck in the real world or absorbed by the virtual world everybody is bragging about? Play this fun game and find out in no time :)\n\nSCR3W DR1VER: A VR Pixel game. Run into the void. Collect the nuggets you need.", "short_description": "GAMEPAD SUPPORTED!\n\nMANCHESTER is a \u201cracing game\u201d, where you have to switch lanes in order to pass obstacles and avoid getting hit by rockets. \n\nFUNNY ARCHITECT: Try to build the biggest tower. The motto is: the biggest, not the highest... The higher you build the easier your tower will collapse.\n\nplus \n-WHERE DO YOU SEE YOURSELF IN 5 YEARS?\n-SCR3W DR1VER\nand WHEEL IN THE SKY"}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.truckervr.com/oculus-privacy-policy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "http://www.truckervr.com/terms-of-service.html", "publisher_name": "Trucker VR", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "http://truckervr.com/", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_MOST", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": null, "context_topics": [], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["ARCADE", "CASUAL", "STRATEGY"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": null, "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["TOUCHPAD", "GAMEPAD", "GEAR_VR_CONTROLLER"], "supported_player_modes": [], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "3177603905857479"}, "review_messages": [""]}]}, "cover_square_image": {"uri": "https://scontent-ams2-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38